2020年6月，米蘭達公開透露，他已經開始為電影創作音樂，其中將有八首[[西班牙語|西班牙語]]和[[英語|英語]]的原創歌曲。電影首映後，他透露他從一開始就一直在為這部電影寫歌。 2021年9月8日，《[[可可夜總會|可可夜總會]]》歌曲的聯合作曲家{{le|傑曼·佛朗哥|Germaine Franco}}開始為電影配樂。<ref>{{Cite tweet |author=Jared Bush|author-link=Jared Bush|user=thejaredbush|number=1435404620495405061|title=I feel so lucky to be surrounded by amazing artists all collectively bringing a new story to life. DAY ONE of score recording is such an incomparable highlight. This score is a triumph. Can’t wait to share who wrote it and for you all to hear it and cry your eyes out.❤️🦋#Encanto}}</ref><ref>{{cite tweet|number=1436422318524272642|user=filmmusicrep|title='Dora and the Lost City of Gold' & 'Tag' composer Germaine Franco scores Walt Disney Animation Studios' 'Encanto'.…<!-- full text of tweet that Twitter returned to the bot (excluding links) added by TweetCiteBot. This may be better truncated or may need expanding (TW limits responses to 140 characters) or case changes. --> |date=September 10, 2021}}</ref>原聲帶於2021年11月19日發行，並在美國公告牌200強中排名第一，成為自《[[冰雪奇緣2|冰雪奇緣2]]》以來第一首登上榜首的迪士尼原聲帶。<ref name="BB200">{{cite magazine|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/chart-beat/encanto-soundtrack-number-one-billboard-200-chart-1235016951/|title='Encanto' Soundtrack Surges to No. 1 on Billboard 200 Chart|magazine=[[Billboard_(magazine)|Billboard]]|last=Caulfield|first=Keith|date=January 9, 2022|access-date=January 9, 2022|archive-date=January 9, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220109213706/https://www.billboard.com/music/chart-beat/encanto-soundtrack-number-one-billboard-200-chart-1235016951/|url-status=live}}</ref>《[[我們不提布魯諾|We Don't Talk About Bruno]]》引起了轟動，並打破了各項記錄，成為迪士尼有史以來最成功的歌曲之一。該曲也攻頂美國[[告示牌百大單曲榜|告示牌百大單曲榜]]和[[英國單曲排行榜|英國單曲排行榜]]，是迪士尼在21世紀的第一首冠軍單曲。<ref>{{Cite web|date=2022-01-21|title=Encanto's We Don't Talk About Bruno becomes first Disney song to reach UK No 1|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2022/jan/21/encanto-we-dont-talk-about-bruno-becomes-first-disney-song-to-reach-uk-no-1|access-date=2022-0