elease-date-2021-disney/ |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.movieinsider.com/m13621/encanto |title=Encanto Movie |last=Renner |first=Brian D. |date=December 13, 2020 |website=Movie Insider |access-date=20 June 2021 |archive-date=23 January 2021 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123181606/https://www.movieinsider.com/m13621/encanto |url-status=live }}</ref>。為應對[[嚴重特殊傳染性肺炎|嚴重特殊傳染性肺炎]]，這部電影在2021年12月24日在[[Disney+|Disney+]]上發布之前進行了為期30天的獨家影院放映<ref>{{cite news|url = https://deadline.com/2021/09/disney-release-dates-eternals-encanto-last-duel-west-side-story-kings-manj-last-duel-1234830827/|title = Disney's ''Eternals, West Side Story, Encanto, Last Duel'' & More to Hit Theaters Ahead of Streaming Bow|work = [[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|last1 = Pedersen|first1 = Erik|last2 = Goldsmith|first2 = Jill|date = September 10, 2021|access-date = October 31, 2021|archive-date = September 10, 2021|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210910212744/https://deadline.com/2021/09/disney-release-dates-eternals-encanto-last-duel-west-side-story-kings-manj-last-duel-1234830827/|url-status = live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Solsman|first=Joan|date=January 7, 2022|title=Pixar's Turning Red is turning Disney back to skipping theaters. What's going on?|url=https://www.cnet.com/tech/services-and-software/disney-plus-disney-marvel-pixar-movie-streaming/|url-status=live|access-date=January 9, 2022|website=[[CNET|CNET]]|archive-date=January 5, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220105144708/https://www.cnet.com/tech/services-and-software/disney-plus-disney-marvel-pixar-movie-streaming/}}</ref>。這部電影與短片《{{le|Far from the Tree|Far from the Tree (film)}}》配對。<ref>{{Cite news|last=Turnquist|first=Kristi|date=January 4, 2022|title=Former Portlander draws on Oregon coast memories for Disney animated short, 'Far From the Tree'|work=[[Oregon_Live|Oregon Live]]|url=https://www.oregonlive.com/entertainment/2022/01/former-portlander-draws-on-oregon-coast-memories-for-disney-animated-short-far-from-the-tree.html|access-date=January 9, 2022|archive-date=January 5, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220105164757/https://www.oregonlive.com/entertainment/2022/01/former-portlander-draws-on-oregon-coast-memories-for-disney-animated-short-far-from-the-tree.html|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Calimbahin|first=Samantha|date=December 22, 2021|title=Far From The Tree Animated Short Trailer Reveals Disney+ Release Date|url=https://screenrant.com/far-from-tree-disney-short-trailer-release-date/|url-status=live|access-date=January 9, 2021|website=Screen Rant|archive-date=December 23, 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211223014654/https://screenrant.com/far-from-tree-disney-short-trailer-release-date/}}</ref>《魔法滿屋》於2022年1月7日在中國上映<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2021/film/news/encanto-paw-patrol-movie-china-release-date-1235144025/|title='Encanto,' 'PAW Patrol: The Movie' to Hit China in January|date=December 28, 2021|author=Rebecca Davis|access-date=December 28, 2021|website=Variety|archive-date=December 28, 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211228202850/https://variety.com/2021/film/news/encanto-paw-patrol-movie-china-release-date-1235144025/|url-status=live}}</ref> 。2022年2月16日，這部電影在獲得Disney+和奧斯卡金像獎提名後在電影院重新上映<ref name="VanHoose">{{cite web |last1=VanHoose |first1=Benjamin |title=Encanto Headed Back to Theaters After Streaming Success and Oscar Nominations |url=https://people.com/movies/encanto-going-back-to-theaters-after-streaming-success |website=[[People_(magazine)|People]] |access-date=February 17, 2022 |language=en |date=February 16, 2022 |archive-date=2022-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220217063800/https://people.com/movies/encanto-going-back-to-theaters-after-streaming-success/ }}</ref>。
===家庭媒體===
《魔法滿屋》於2021年12月24日在 Disney+上發布，並由[[華特迪士尼家庭娛樂公司|華特迪士尼家庭娛樂公司]]於2022年2月8日發行[[DVD-Video|DVD-Video]]、[[藍光光碟|藍光光碟]]和[[超高畫質藍光光碟|超高畫質藍光光碟]]。精彩花絮包括“Let’s Talk About Bruno”、“Our-{ Casita}-”、“Journey To Colombia”、“Familia Lo Es Todo”、“A Journey Through Music”，以及電影的sing-along版本<ref>{{Cite web|last=King|first=Aidan|date=December 13, 2021|title='Encanto' 4K, Blu-ray, Digital Release Includes Sing-Along Version|url=https://collider.com/encanto-4k-bluray-digital-release-date-bonus-content/|access-date=February 17, 2022|website=Collider|archive-date=2022-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220217133527/https://collider.com/encanto-4k-bluray-digital-release-date-bonus-content/}}</ref> 。《{{le|Far from the Tree|Far from the Tree (film)}}》也與電影一起在實體媒體上發布。<ref name="#1">{{Cite web|last=Schaefer|first=Sandy|date=December 13, 2021|title=Encanto Hits Digital Just In Time For Christmas, Blu-Ray Early Next Year|url=https://www.slashfilm.com/705482/encanto-hits-digital-just-in-time-for-christmas-blu-ray-early-next-year/|access-date=February 17, 2022|website=/Film|archive-date=2022-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220217133527/https://www.slashfilm.com/705482/encanto-hits-digital-just-in-time-for-christmas-blu-ray-early-next-year/}}</ref>

自Disney+發布以來，《魔法滿屋》一直在[[尼爾森收視率|尼爾森收視率]]的每周流媒體排行榜上名列前茅，最近的總觀看時間為14億分鐘。<ref name="#1"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2022/02/encanto-tops-nielsen-streaming-chart-hotel-transylvania-transformania-1234931648/|title=‘Encanto’ Tops Nielsen Streaming Chart, With ‘Hotel Transylvania: Transformania’ A Strong No. 3|website=Deadline|date=February 11, 2022|author=Dade Hayes|access-date=February 24, 2022|archive-date=2022-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220524074714/https://deadline.com/2022/02/encanto-tops-nielsen-streaming-chart-hotel-transylvania-transformania-1234931648/}}</ref>

=== 評價 ===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據200條評論，持有91%的新鮮度，平均得分7.5／10，觀眾投票獲得93%的分數，平均得分為4.6／5<ref>{{Cite Rotten Tomatoes|title=Encanto|id=encanto_2021|type=movie|access-date=2021-11-24}}</ref>，在該網站排名2021年度第三高評價的動畫電影<ref>{{cite web|title=BEST ANIMATED MOVIES 2021|url=https://editorial.rottentomatoes.com/guide/best-movies-2021/|accessdate=2022-05-14|author=|date=|format=|publisher=|language=en|website=[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]|archive-date=2022-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220111123651/https://editorial.rottentomatoes.com/guide/best-movies-2021/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，電影根據41條評論，獲得75分（滿分100分）<ref>{{Cite Metacritic|id=encanto-2021|type=movie|title=Encanto|access-date=2021-11-24}}</ref>。在首映周末，據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的平均評價於A+至F間落於「A」，而{{le|PostTrak|PostTrak}}的調查結果則顯示，有88％的觀眾給初正面評價，其中70％的觀眾表示絕對會推薦<ref name=opening/>。<ref name="opening">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2021/11/encanto-house-of-gucci-resident-evil-thanksgiving-box-office-1234880192/|title=The Sobering Reality of Thanksgiving Box Office During Pandemic with ''Encanto'' Sans ''Top Gun 2''; Adults Return for ''House Of Gucci'', ''Licorice Pizza''|date=November 27, 2021|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|access-date=November 28, 2021|archive-date=November 25, 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211125222254/https://deadline.com/2021/11/encanto-house-of-gucci-resident-evil-thanksgiving-box-office-1234880192/|url-status=live}}</ref>。

[[網際網路電影資料庫|網際網路電影資料庫]]評選2021年最佳動畫電影中，《魔法滿屋》排名第3名<ref>{{cite web|url=https://m.imdb.com/list/ls552669373/|title=Best Animated Movie of 2021|website=[[IMDb|IMDb]]|accessdate=2022-05-14|archive-date=2022-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220601050232/https://m.imdb.com/list/ls552669373/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
截至2022年3月11日，《魔法滿屋》在美國和加拿大的總票房為9570萬美元，在其他地區為1.531億美元，全球總票房為2.488億美元。在被《歡樂好聲音2》超越之前，《魔法滿屋》是2021年票房最高的動畫電影<ref name=":6">{{Cite web|last=Clark|first=Travis|title=The top animated movies at the US box office this year show that families haven't rushed back to theaters|url=https://www.businessinsider.com/highest-grossing-animated-movies-at-the-box-office-2021-12|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211231042358/https://www.businessinsider.com/highest-grossing-animated-movies-at-the-box-office-2021-12|archive-date=December 31, 2021|access-date=2022-01-02|website=Business Insider|language=en-US}}</ref><ref name=":7">{{Cite web|last=Rubin|first=Rebecca|date=January 23, 2022|title='Spider-Man: No Way Home' Returns to No. 1 on Box Office Charts in Sixth Weekend of Release|url=https://variety.com/2022/film/box-office/spiderman-no-way-home-box-office-beats-scream-1235160913/|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220123165712/https://variety.com/2022/film/box-office/spiderman-no-way-home-box-office-beats-scream-1235160913/|archive-date=January 23, 2022|access-date=January 23, 2022|website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|quote=''Sing 2'' has generated $128 million at the domestic box office and $241 million globally, making it the highest-grossing animated film in pandemic times. The movie surpassed Disney’s ''Encanto'' ($223 million) and Universal’s ''Croods: A New Age'' ($227 million) to notch that benchmark.}}</ref>。考慮到電影的製作預算和營銷費用，以及影院在收入中的份額，據估計，《魔法滿屋》在全球範圍內至少需要3億美元才能實現收支平衡<ref>{{cite web|url=https://dailycampus.com/2021/11/30/box-office-breakdown-encanto-brings-its-magic-to-the-charts/|title=Box Office Breakdown: ''Encanto'' brings its magic to the charts|date=November 30, 2021|first=Zachary|last=Wisnefsky|website=[[The_Daily_Campus|The Daily Campus]]|access-date=December 25, 2021|archive-date=December 25, 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211225005437/https://dailycampus.com/2021/11/30/box-office-breakdown-encanto-brings-its-magic-to-the-charts/|url-status=live}}</ref>。然而，這部電影在2021年的聖誕節假期裡走紅了，並在2021年12月24日向Disney+數字發布後取得了更廣泛的商業成功。<ref name=":10">{{Cite news|last=Collin|first=Robbie|date=2022-01-14|title=Disney's Encanto is a huge hit – and that's bad news for Pixar|language=en-GB|work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Telegraph]]|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/films/2022/01/14/disneys-encanto-huge-hit-bad-news-pixar/|url-status=live|url-access=subscription|access-date=2022-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220114215839/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/films/2022/01/14/disneys-encanto-huge-hit-bad-news-pixar/|archive-date=January 14, 2022|issn=0307-1235}}</ref><ref name=":9">{{Cite web|last=Colangelo|first=B. J.|date=2022-01-10|title=The Encanto Soundtrack Is Now The Biggest Thing In The World|url=https://www.slashfilm.com/729755/the-encanto-soundtrack-is-now-the-biggest-thing-in-the-world/|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220113114608/https://www.slashfilm.com/729755/the-encanto-soundtrack-is-now-the-biggest-thing-in-the-world/|archive-date=January 13, 2022|access-date=2022-01-13|website=[[奇幻魔法屋/Film|奇幻魔法屋//Film]]|language=en-US}}</ref><ref name=":4">{{Cite news|last=Niazi|first=Amil|date=January 14, 2022|title=Parents are losing their minds. Time to watch 'Encanto.' Again.|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/parenting/2022/01/14/watching-encanto-again/|url-access=subscription|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220114161756/https://www.washingtonpost.com/parenting/2022/01/14/watching-encanto-again/|archive-date=January 14, 2022|access-date=January 14, 2022|newspaper=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]}}</ref>
